Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:27.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}心神不定  因为我犹豫不决
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.87,0:00:31.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}轻微的颤抖着  control过了还在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:35.39,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太阳也好  运气（月亮）也罢  完全与我无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:36.80,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}“只有硬上了吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:39.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我这样劝说自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:45.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}情况很糟糕  临阵逃脱又没毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:49.07,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}虽然前途未卜  也只能靠胆量获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:52.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}压制着冲动  寻找敌我之间的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.76,0:00:55.85,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}唯一需要的是胜利的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:00:58.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能尝下胜利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.96,0:01:02.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}或者喝下满腔的苦水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:06.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的  一切都是二择其一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:10.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}好想操纵命运的轮盘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:15.75,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}绝好的黄金时间  亲自把握机会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.75,0:01:19.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}摆出一副扑克脸  设下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:24.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}把敌人引入幻想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:31.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}无尽的pressure game  跨越过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:35.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为了跨越荣耀的borderline
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:39.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}How many？  我需要支付多少代价？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:44.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}到底舍不得放弃哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:38.78,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,250)\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:45.64,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,500)\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.77,0:22:48.32,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}谈话直到日出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.32,0:22:51.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}牵手直到日落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.15,0:22:56.40,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2\i1}就这样明天后天也一直这样形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.49,0:23:00.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}寂寞的看着街上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.95,0:23:06.30,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一个人是无法找到温暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.30,0:23:11.79,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}第一次知道爱原来可以如此坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.97,0:23:17.64,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}那是在与你相遇之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:22.88,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:28.19,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.19,0:23:33.39,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为一个人无法入睡  也无法做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:39.16,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在不安无法到达的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.16,0:23:44.42,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}即使是没有星星的夜晚也要继续将其照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.66,0:23:46.92,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}和你在一起的话能到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:49.92,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}一个人无法走过的道路  如果是两个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:52.96,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\i1}就可以哼着歌走过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.96,0:23:56.38,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2\i1}只要有你在就很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}520先士的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来他知道马可也参加了歼灭战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有新情报来了我会告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大总统辅佐就像是做人质一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果乐观点看的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁机在大总统睡觉的时候取下他的首级
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.07,0:02:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给大佐的传话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡还在到处转悠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.05,0:02:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你告诉我伊修瓦尔的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在伊修瓦尔发生了那样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有的事情都告诉了我这样的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术师是追求真理的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却不知道身边的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐在想达成目的之后的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达成目的之后…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 你恢复原来的身体后想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 想吃温莉的苹果派
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为脑子里已经塞满了恢复原来的身体这个目的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 先跟婆婆还有师傅打招呼 告诉他们“回来了”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 一直受她们照顾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家会笑着迎接我们的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到大家的笑脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然情况很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是感觉有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有好消息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的炼金术无法发动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同一个时间 地上似乎也无法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 那个小女孩和斯卡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有他们能用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的炼金术里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我们不知道的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还没完全走到死胡同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了？那个豆丁女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 今天一大早就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 她说去哪了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在整个中央都市？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且完全没有线索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然有线索了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探病礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要送就送那种有很多美女照片的杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们离开的期间里 可别偷懒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我去品尝一下西部的著名料理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃一些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长大后要变强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我离开的期间里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保护好大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利曹长 好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔蔓准尉 还没有出发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来向大佐还东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在中央都市的勤务时间真是短暂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曹长是南方司令部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 正好相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北方司令部一定很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利曹长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 期待再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进来了 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来取忘记的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡好像还在中央都市里晃悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可得小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且技术好的护卫已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你操劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我跟错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你认为错了就一枪毙了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是那天的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在允许的范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉可真温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作的时候可不要偷懒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兵也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 应该说是兴趣增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,象也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我很光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为脑子不好 进士官学校可是费了很大的劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果您希望 会一直跟您到地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇后也被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 将军的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…是这种猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在寻找带着这家伙的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}（你知道吗 知道的话请告诉我）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 那边那个异类就放一边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 没有黑白猫的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许已经不在中央都市了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 清的炼丹术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也问问别人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是不想欠大佐人情的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 说起欠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把钱还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好前面 前面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少 500先士？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,520先士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想糊弄过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 这么精打细算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可成不了大人物的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是继续借着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等大佐做了大总统之后再还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁告诉你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍克爱中尉 还有伊修瓦尔的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱就算一直借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会让你还给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 到那个时候会再问你借零钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说等实行民主制了再还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那个也还了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就再借一次 定个约定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 我必须活得相当久才行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 别让中尉再担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你送我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真慢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都等得不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真精神 瓦涅莎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了 罗伊小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好 耶诞节夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了提提精神来玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为病刚好 酒不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一个特别的 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拉曼阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:11:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位名叫耶诞节夫人的女性从中央都市打来的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 别把极密线路的号码告诉普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我还没被抛弃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指名要我这老头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能保护好少主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是这副样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也算被姚家选上的守护一族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道廉耻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可是伤员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有…手臂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋…笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和兰芳的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要给她介绍机械铠技师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的好意我们心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不需要进一步的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机械铠技师我们自己会想办法找的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不能放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人看到了兰芳的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再把你们的熟人卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了您 孙女的性命保住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是个被人感谢的医生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺克斯医生 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快…快点出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没好到把麻烦一直留在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝陛下的身体状况似乎在恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要尽快夺回少主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着长生不老之法回国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等着 魔窟的住人们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会忘记你的救命之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺克斯医生 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今 装成医生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我这么个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好 父亲 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公 还精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有重要的事来到附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是瘦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是瘦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作很忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还是老样子对着尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这周治疗了两个活着的患者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然去救助人命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 我现在以医生为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道父亲自伊修瓦尔以来一直很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使这样 父亲也没有放弃做医生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢作为医生的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然做得不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝杯咖啡再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱得一塌糊涂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 趁你父亲泡咖啡的时候 我们收拾一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真有神存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是我这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和家人一起喝咖啡这点幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:15:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是可以拥有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样伊修瓦尔就完全进入国军的管辖了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了 金普利少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无视等价交换 实现了超越想像的炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详细情况写成文书后提交
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头还给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么 金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这样知道贤者之石所在的只有你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来 金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被释放了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别问多余的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面的命令吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你杀了五个士官却没被判死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你使了什么招？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是我的人望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别笑死人了 炸弹狂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然释放你这种发狂的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面的人到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看守先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么长时间受你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我取下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊的玩具 送给你的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了 金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你出狱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是你们的命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 因为人手不够
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说会给我工作吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:19:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得马可医生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作了贤者之石的研究者吧 我记得他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个马可也许
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有完全确定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看门的合成兽少了一头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可是擅长生物炼成的炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也许是替身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且更麻烦的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可能和伊修瓦尔人斯卡一起逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为实行了伊修瓦尔歼灭战的红莲之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.98,0:19:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我手下漏掉的伊修瓦尔人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不可原谅的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现斯卡杀死也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是马可要带来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只为了这点事把我叫出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果抓住了马可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以儆效尤 毁掉一座城市给他看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错的工作吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真会做肮脏的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来能用上这久违的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要毁灭一个城市 那个或许不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？又用了伊修瓦尔人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是马克医生的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直研究着石头的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是肮脏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么放我走？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有事要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那个叫金普利的炼金术师之事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长留下的研究书里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我无法理解的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究书？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长临死之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说这个国家的炼金术很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这点 应该有记载
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是优秀的炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能解读吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家的炼金术 很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人 那个女孩回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯卡先生 您没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴增加了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.75,0:21:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他名叫马可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是制作贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协助伊修瓦尔歼灭战的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石是？长生不老的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可先生 你知道石头的制作方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.59,0:21:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做的？请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 不要追求那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只破坏了脸的表面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.45,0:22:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他止血
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸还是破坏得看不出是你比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.73,0:22:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}（不要紧吗 马可先生）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去我藏了兄长的研究书之地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.51,0:22:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.76,0:24:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐藏着的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.55,0:24:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和微笑一同出现
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.21,0:24:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的火苗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降临在错综的中央都市
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.41,0:24:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.02,0:24:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.64,0:24:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第32话 大总统的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.20,0:24:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道反而会比较幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.55,0:24:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说…
